STATE of North Carolina
v.
Jamey J.C. CHEEK. No. 577A97-3. Supreme Court of North Carolina. April 1, 2004. Michael L. Unti, Sharon L. Smith, John G. Barnwell, Assistant Attorney General for Cheek. John Carriker, District Attorney, for State.

ORDER

Upon consideration of the petition filed by Defendant on the 11th day of December 2003 in this matter for a writ of certiorari to review the order of the Superior Court, New Hanover County, the following order was entered and is hereby certified to the Superior Court of that County:

"Denied by order of the Court in conference, this the 1st day of April 2004."
